c: 7
v: 203
t: "Nabiyow ama koros Astootik Asta keenih baahe waytek atu isih tet ginteh macah tet baahe waytaa? kok iyyan, Nabiyow keenik ixxic: woh yol tanim hinna cagalah anu kataatam Yi Rabbik wacyih yol obsimtaama, ama Qhuraanay siinil akriye sin Rabbik Baxxaqqa iyya sumaaqay anu nummâ farmoyta kinniyoomuh Asta yoh yakke kinni, usuk yeemene marah tirtoo kee Racmata"